{"tid":2057304,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[達爾文獎2020]  洞穴口欄杆倒立跌死 澳洲男子獲獎","createTime":"2020-06-09T09:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T05:43:14.000Z","uid":89679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"82c56c8273166324f025626f1d4d3fa0bbf9d546","tid":2057304,"uid":89679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8zAYK6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8zAYK6.jpg&h=e6a80406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n達爾文獎官方網站介紹呢個獎項:「為了紀念進化之父查爾斯&middot;達爾文 (Charles Darwin)，達爾文獎 (Darwin Awards) 旨在紀念那些通過以最壯觀的方式，將自己從基因庫中剔除而改善我們的基因庫的人。」<br />\n<br />\n2020年「達爾文獎」得主有兩位，除了日本網台主播 Tedzu，無裝備下攀登富士山跌死獲獎之外，仲有呢位澳洲20歲男子 Bradley Streeter。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WuHOziG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuHOziG.jpg&h=f18fdf6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲城市芒特甘比爾 (Mount Gambier) 有個「花園洞穴」(Cave Gardens Sinkhole)。洞穴屬大自然景觀，洞穴淡水曾經供應全市食用。因為呢度具有歷史意義，而且風景優美，所以成為國家級自然遺產，係旅遊名勝。<br />\n<br />\n2020年2月，澳洲男子 Bradley Streeter，凌晨12點同朋友倚住欄杆欣賞洞穴期間，突然雙手壓住欄杆話要做倒立。點知一時錯手，跌落深30米嘅淡水洞穴，消防員搜索至凌晨3點，先搵到佢嘅屍體。<br />\n<br />\n當地市長話，呢個景點嘅位置絕對唔危險，咁多年亦無發生意外，所以對於 Bradley 嘅意外感到遺憾之餘，亦覺得有啲驚奇。<br />\n<br />\n「達爾文獎」評委會，就向 Bradley 頒發「A Slack-Robatic Effort」大獎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgEtziO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgEtziO.jpg&h=363e38a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢件事，不其然令人諗起飛鵝山瑜伽男女，如果佢哋跌咗落山，唔知會唔會得到達爾文獎呢?"},{"pid":"06f3d05586c9ba0b267dd6cd0495e2657ea89694","tid":2057304,"uid":89679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:28:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fitz.hk/life/travel/%e9%81%94%e7%88%be%e6%96%87%e7%8d%8e2020-%e6%b4%9e%e7%a9%b4%e5%8f%a3%e6%ac%84%e6%9d%86%e5%80%92%e7%ab%8b%e8%b7%8c%e6%ad%bb-%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e7%8d%b2%e7%8d%8e/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2Flife%2Ftravel%2F%25e9%2581%2594%25e7%2588%25be%25e6%2596%2587%25e7%258d%258e2020-%25e6%25b4%259e%25e7%25a9%25b4%25e5%258f%25a3%25e6%25ac%2584%25e6%259d%2586%25e5%2580%2592%25e7%25ab%258b%25e8%25b7%258c%25e6%25ad%25bb-%25e6%25be%25b3%25e6%25b4%25b2%25e7%2594%25b7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e7%258d%25b2%25e7%258d%258e%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=cde463f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://fitz.hk/life/travel/%e9%81%94%e7%88%be%e6%96%87%e7%8d%8e2020-%e6%b4%9e%e7%a9%b4%e5%8f%a3%e6%ac%84%e6%9d%86%e5%80%92%e7%ab%8b%e8%b7%8c%e6%ad%bb-%e6%be%b3%e6%b4%b2%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e7%8d%b2%e7%8d%8e/</a>"},{"pid":"b2fd5f138177c989a12e7b72202c45e309fdb447","tid":2057304,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蠢人獎？"},{"pid":"8d88693ca0bfa83ae5d538ff888da6995ddb69be","tid":2057304,"uid":236716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:22:33.000Z","msg":"其實有無咁多年以嚟嘅得獎名單？google 過都係得出名嗰幾單"},{"pid":"7011b9f551599b3fd5acd23c10f7f6ba864e4bc9","tid":2057304,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"